text_lines.line_text: DISTRIBUTION: EFFECTIVENESS OF PRE-SELL (REPORT ON FEB. 17 ONLY).
% OF DISTRIBUTION ACHIEVED IN RETAIL OUTLETS:
HAS PROVEN TO BE AN EXCELLENT TOOL IN GENERATING PACK TRIAL IN
BOTH HIGH AND LOW DEVELOPMENT PRICE VALUE MARKETS. MANY
ADDITIONAL SUPPLY WOULD BE HELPFUL. INITIAL QUANTITIES
CARTON MOVEMENT SPOTTY AT THIS POINT. SUPPLIES ARE MORE THAN
ADEQUATE AND THE NEED IS MOSTLY PACKAGE SUPPORT AT THIS TIME.
EFFECTIVENESS OF ADVERTISING: OUTDOOR AND PRINT ADS HAVE BEEN EFFECTIVE IN
CREATING CONSUMER AWARENESS IN THOSE DIVISIONS WITH ADVERTISING. BILLBOARDS
ARE EYE CATCHING AND CONSUMERS ARE MORE AWARE OF THE PRODUCT IN THOSE MARKETS
